    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:mb@marc-borer.ch">mb@marc-borer.ch</a></p>

    <h2>Responsible for Content</h2>
    <p>Marc Borer, at the address stated above.</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      The author assumes no liability for the correctness, accuracy, timeliness,
      reliability, or completeness of the information provided on this website.
    </p>
    <p>
      Liability claims against the author for damages of a material or immaterial nature
